<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="it">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Sostenibilità e Riciclo | Brand Name</title>
    <style>
        :root { --main-color: #1a1a1a; --text-light: #666; --bg: #ffffff; }
        body { font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; margin: 0; background: var(--bg); color: var(--main-color); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; }
        
        /* Hero Section */
        .hero { padding: 80px 20px; text-align: center; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; }
        .hero h1 { font-size: 2.5rem; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: -1px; margin-bottom: 10px; text-transform: uppercase; }
        .hero p { color: var(--text-light); font-size: 1.1rem; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; }

        /* Image Section (Simile a Carandini) */
        .product-img { width: 100%; max-height: 500px; object-fit: cover; margin: 40px 0; }

        /* Recycling Info Section */
        .info-section { max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 60px 20px; }
        .grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 40px; }
        @media (max-width: 600px) { .grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }

        .item { border-top: 1px solid #eee; padding-top: 20px; }
        .item h3 { font-size: 0.9rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 2px; margin-bottom: 15px; color: #999; }
        .item p { font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0; }
        .material-code { font-weight: bold; color: var(--main-color); margin-top: 10px; display: block; }

        /* Footer */
        .footer { padding: 100px 20px 40px; text-align: center; font-size: 0.8rem; letter-spacing: 1px; color: #ccc; text-transform: uppercase; }
        
        .btn-contact { display: inline-block; margin-top: 40px; padding: 15px 40px; border: 1px solid #000; text-decoration: none; color: #000; transition: 0.3s; font-size: 0.8rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 2px; }
        .btn-contact:hover { background: #000; color: #fff; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <section class="hero">
        <h1>Sostenibilità</h1>
        <p>Il nostro impegno per il futuro passa attraverso gesti quotidiani. Ecco come smaltire correttamente questo pack.</p>
    </section>

    <img src="pack.jpg" alt="Packaging" class="product-img" onerror="this.style.display='none'">

    <section class="info-section">
        <div class="grid">
            <div class="item">
                <h3>Contenitore</h3>
                <p>Vetro Bianco Premium</p>
                <span class="material-code">GL 70 • VETRO</span>
            </div>
            <div class="item">
                <h3>Tappo</h3>
                <p>Legno e Sughero naturale</p>
                <span class="material-code">FOR 51 • ORGANICO</span>
            </div>
            <div class="item">
                <h3>Etichetta</h3>
                <p>Carta FSC certificata</p>
                <span class="material-code">PAP 22 • CARTA</span>
            </div>
            <div class="item">
                <h3>Sigillo</h3>
                <p>Plastica termoretraibile</p>
                <span class="material-code">PVC 03 • PLASTICA</span>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div style="text-align: center;">
            <a href="mailto:info@tuobrand.com" class="btn-contact">Contattaci</a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer class="footer">
        © 2026 Sustainable Packaging Initiative
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
